#!/usr/bin/env bash

cat <<'EOF'
joinmarket-node — manage a JoinMarket daemon for Bitcoin CoinJoin

COMMANDS
  daemon start     Start joinmarket daemon
  daemon stop      Stop joinmarket daemon
  daemon status    Check if joinmarket is running
  daemon monitor   Tail the daemon log
  daemon install   Install joinmarket (via pip)
  daemon enable    Install + configure as system service
  daemon disable   Stop service and remove unit

USAGE
  joinmarket-node daemon status
  joinmarket-node daemon enable
  joinmarket-node daemon start

JOINMARKET PROVIDES
  - Bitcoin CoinJoin transactions (maker/taker)
  - Privacy via collaborative transactions
  - Yield generation for makers

SERVICES
  Wallet RPC:  http://127.0.0.1:28183

FILES
  Config:    /etc/joinmarket/
  Data:      /var/lib/joinmarket/
  Logs:      /var/log/joinmarket/

REQUIREMENTS
  - Python 3.7+
  - Bitcoin Core (for wallet backend)
  - pip3 (for installation)

SEE ALSO
  https://github.com/JoinMarket-Org/joinmarket-clientserver
EOF